Notes:

To install and connect the MYSQL in the DB using node.js:
  run in the terminal: npm install mysql2

To encrypt passwords:
  run: npm install bcrypt

To DB credentials:
  run: npm install dotenv

To use sessions in Express:
  run: npm install express-session

To install multer for handling file uploads:
  run: npm install multer

